<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.7.2">
<l>nīḷvāṉ kuṟaḷuruvāy niṉṟirantu māvalimaṇ</l>
<l>tāḷā laḷaviṭṭa takkaṇaikku mikkāṉai</l>
<l>tōḷāta māmaṇiyait toṇṭark kiṉiyāṉai</l>
<l>kēḷāc cevikaḷ ceviyalla kēṭṭāmē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Ears that do not hear of the one who is sweet to [his] devotees,</l>
<l>The great, impervious jewel, the one who was too large</l>
<l>For Māvali’s offering when he measured the earth with his feet,</l>
<l>Having stood begging in the shape of a dwarf so to [then] enlarge,</l>
<l rend="indent">are not ears; [this] we have heard.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
